    "Description": "A rival crew was able to get their hands on our delivery routes and now they have one of my cargo ships pinned down at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>.\n\nNow the ship\u2019s sitting there being guarded by a full crew of these assholes. They must be waiting for someone to show up with a transport ship, but you\u2019re going to get there first.\n\nHead there with a crew of your own and a <EM4>heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4> to take the goods away. Make sure they\u2019re the best people you got. It\u2019d be a mistake to underestimate these bastards.\n\nGhost them and bring my cargo back to the freight elevator at <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4> and I\u2019ll make sure you\u2019re seriously comp\u2019d for this.\n\n-Twitch",
